{"tid":1220703,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港真係好靚好靚","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:31:43.000Z","uid":4050,"like":96,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a53a4331315bfd7118a78a3905e0459199c1ee","tid":1220703,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"呢幾日既香港真係好靚，坐飛機返黎既時候真係好感觸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">廣州及廣州白雲機場</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W7nOyGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW7nOyGX.png&h=a2504c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S57u2Ak.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS57u2Ak.png&h=aeb5d42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">珠江三角洲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SvP2AR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SvP2AR.png&h=ce52a0b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">澳門及港珠澳大橋</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OxYBHBk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxYBHBk.png&h=008740a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港島/九龍/沙田</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZFsPgO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZFsPgO.png&h=05741078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuQXr3u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuQXr3u.png&h=80a709c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.